The Chicco Space Baby Walker is a great entertainment centre that can help your child learn to walk. From a certain point onwards, kids don't want to crawl any more, they want to walk. They can reach everything better and are faster. This process of learning is long and requires patience. As children don't usually have this patience yet, you can support the development process by providing a baby walker to help your child along. The little learner-walker can experience a feeling of success and can learn to walk without having to hold your hand all the time. The Chicco Space Baby Walker contains a veritable entertainment miracle. There's an MP3 connection for your MP3-player so you can play your child's favourite songs and tunes. The music centre encourages your child to press buttons and reach out. This is particularly important for developing the child's fine motor skills because the buttons needs to be pressed in a targeted way. The frame of the Chicco Space Baby Walker is height adjustable so it can be adapted to your child's size. The baby walker can grow with your child and both small and bigger children can benefit from this colourful toy. It's important that your child can have both feet on the floor so he or she can walk. The Chicco Space is suitable for kids from the age of six months and your little treasure can play with it until he or she weighs 12 kg. To ensure your child can sit comfortably, the seat is padded extra well. The high backrest provides support for your child's back and ensures stability and a secure posture.

Neptune car seat is homologated for use in cars to ECE R44/04 Standards for Groups 1/2/3, for children from 9 to 36 kg (from 1 to around 12 years of age). Neptune allows you to use the car for many years to come: the ergonomic and practical pommel makes it easy to regulate both the height of the safety belts (Group 1 only, up to 18 Kg) and the headrest; this will ensure your child travels safely and comfortably for as long as he uses the seat. Group 1 children (9-18 kg) must be fastened in using the car seat safety straps Group 2 and 3 children can be fastened in using the standard car safety belts. Chicco - Relax And Play Colors Cot Mobile

Relax & Play Colors Cot Mobile is the first mobile for playing, sleeping, dreaming. 

Its elves have been studied following indications from the Chicco Colors Research. During the firsts 15 days of its life, the newborn distinguishes the green elf colour contrasts. After the first months its eyes will start to perceive the red elf also. After the fourth month, baby can see weaker contrasts like yellow for example. The musical console can be separated.

The Cot Mobile relaxes and entertains baby thanks to its 2 modes of operation: 

  1. Relax is in the lights and in the music. Warm and suffused lights, pleasant and relaxing music...the Colors Cot Mobile musical console sweetly accompanies baby to sleep
  2. Play is in the colours and movement. The coloured elves rotate slowly, the baby observes them with curiosity. As the baby grows up, it will amuse itself in discovering the colours, seeing the elves circle and following the absorbing classical music melodies
  3. Develops Musical Skills: A sweet melody relaxes and reassures the baby
  4. Develops Visual Skills: The lights accompany the baby into a world of dreams
  5. Develops Musical Skills: Fun melodies entertain the baby in the cot
  6. Helps the Development of Chromatic perception: The colors of each elf have been selected to help the progressive development of baby's sight
  7. Separable Music Box: Up to 15 minutes of classical music provide either relaxation or entertainment for the baby
  8. Night Light: Reassures the baby whilst it is sleeping

Product Description

Graco's SnugRide® Click Connect™ 30 is an ultra-lightweight infant car seat, making it easy for you to carry baby from car to stroller and everywhere in between. The seat is designed to protect a rear-facing baby from 4 - 30 lbs. and features a comfortable seat to keep baby safe and cozy. It's is equipped with Click Connect technology, providing a secure one-step attachment to all Graco Click Connect strollers so you can create a custom travel system that best fits your lifestyle. It's an excellent first car seat to help protect your precious child.

Specifications

      Weight without base: 7 lbs

      Weight with base: 11 lbs

      Dimensions:

    Length: 26.75", Width: 17.5", Height: 14"

Care and Maintenance

      • Machine-washable seat cushion
      • Metal and plastic parts may be cleaned with mild soap and water
      • Buckle may be cleaned with a damp cloth

To Unbuckle Harness:
      1. Lift the lever and pull the shoulder harness straps to loosen the harness
      2. Tilt the top of the buckle toward the child's abdomen
      3. Press in at the top of the red button
      4. Pull tongues out of the buckle

Harness Buckle Cleaning Process:
    Turn the restraint over and push the retainer through the harness strap slot to remove the buckle from the car seat. Place the buckle in a cup of warm water upside down and gently agitate the buckle, pressing the red button several times while it is in the water. Do not submerge the harness webbing and do not use soaps or lubricants, only rinse the harness buckle with warm water. Shake out the excess water and allow the harness buckle to air dry. Reattach the harness buckle into the same slot and re-check harness for correct installation according to the car seat manual before use.​

Recommended Use

    Rear-Facing Only. For children 4-30 lbs. and up to 30 inches.

Care and Maintenance

      • Machine-washable seat cushion
      • Metal and plastic parts may be cleaned with mild soap and water
      • Buckle may be cleaned with a damp cloth

To Unbuckle Harness:
      1. Lift the lever and pull the shoulder harness straps to loosen the harness
      2. Tilt the top of the buckle toward the child's abdomen
      3. Press in at the top of the red button
      4. Pull tongues out of the buckle

Harness Buckle Cleaning Process:
    Turn the restraint over and push the retainer through the harness strap slot to remove the buckle from the car seat. Place the buckle in a cup of warm water upside down and gently agitate the buckle, pressing the red button several times while it is in the water. Do not submerge the harness webbing and do not use soaps or lubricants, only rinse the harness buckle with warm water. Shake out the excess water and allow the harness buckle to air dry. Reattach the harness buckle into the same slot and re-check harness for correct installation according to the car seat manual before use.

Recommended Use

    • Rear-facing only
    • For infants 5-22 lbs and up to 29"
    To make usage requirements simpler for caregivers, Graco is updating their in car handle usage requirements for all rear facing only CRs. Graco now allows the use of the handle in any locked position on Graco Infant SafeSeat, SnugRide Classic Connect 22, SnugRide Classic Connect 30, SnugRide Classic Connect 32, SnugRide Classic Connect 35 and the new SnugRide Click Connect 35 and SnugRide Click Connect 40. This change does not apply in Canada, where the handle must always be used locked in the upright position

Group 0+ Car Seats: You should keep a baby in a group 0+ rear-facing car seat for as long as possible as this is the safest way of transporting your baby in the car. You should only move them onto the next car seat once they have reached the weight limit of that seat, or the crown of their head is level with the top of the car seat. The weight limits may vary so please ensure you have read the labels on the side of the seat which will tell you your specific seats limits.

Suitability: When buying a car seat its important to make sure you are choosing the correct one for both your car and your child. It’s important you select the correct type of car seat for your child’s weight and because not all car seats will fit all cars it is critical that you check the selected car seat will fit your model of car. Follow the instructions provided with your chosen seat carefully for a safe and accurate fitting of the car seat and make sure you have the instructions to hand for future reference. Your car manual will also provide guidance on any fitting guidance specific to that car model.

Free Car Seat Demonstration In Store: All our Babies R Us stores have advisors trained to fit car seats and check that the car seat you are considering is the right one for your car and your child. They will happily demonstrate how to fit it safely. We offer this securefit service because we know how important it is to keep your child safe on all your car journeys.

Product Details

From the moment your baby arrives, you realise you want to protect him the best you can. The Graco Coast car seat helps you to keep your baby safe in the car and is classed as a group 1, making it suitable for children weighing between 9 and 18kg. A 5-point safety harness and reinforced side impact protection provides the optimum safety for your child.

5 reclining positions ensure your child is comfortable at all times and the lock-off system ensures your child is positioned correctly. Extra protection is provided by the performance harness, which is doubled with anti-slip material to absorb energy during a crash. As your child grows the back of the Graco Coast seat can be removed and it can be used as a low booster seat.

Graco® 4Ever™ All-in-One Car Seat - Kylie

Graco's 4Ever All-in-One Car Seat, in Kylie, gives you 10 years with one car seat. It's comfortable for your child and convenient for you as it transitions from rear-facing in a harness for your infant (4 - 40 lbs.) to a forward-facing, five-point harness seat (20 - 65 lbs.) to a high-back, belt-positioning booster (30 - 100 lbs.) to a backless, belt-positioning booster (40 - 120 lbs.). For a proper fit, the Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System and 10-position headrest let you adjust the harness and headrest together, with no rethreading. The six-position recline keeps your child comfortable, while the InRight™ LATCH system with one-second attachment makes installation easy. It's the only seat that truly goes from baby to booster!

Product Highlights

  • This four-in-one car seat gives you 10 years of use! It seamlessly transforms from rear-facing in a harness for your infant (4 - 40 lbs.), to a forward-facing harness car seat (20 - 65 lbs.), to high back belt-positioning booster (30 - 100 lbs.), to a backless, belt-positioning booster (40 - 120 lbs.). It's the only seat around that can take your child from baby to booster!
  • Six-position recline adjusts to fit and keep your growing child comfortable; it's comfy for them and convenient for you

  • One-hand, 10-position head rest makes it easy to give your growing child a proper fit for optimal safety
  • Graco's exclusive InRight LATCH attachment provides an easy, one-second LATCH attachment with an audio click cue to help ensure secure installation.
  • The 4Ever is side-impact tested for occupant retention solely with the built-in five-point harness system.
  • The all-in-one car seat is engineered and crash tested to meet or exceed US standard FMVSS 213. This standard includes New Car Assessment Program (NCAP) with peak crash force approximately two times the car seat standard, Extreme Car Interior Temperatures and Side Impact Tested.
  • The washable seat cover is easy to remove without removing the harness.
  • Steel-reinforced frame provides strength and durability for years of smart utility.
  • Integrated harness storage compartment holds the harness straps that are not in use while in the belt positioning booster mode for a simple transition back to harness mode.
  • Easy-to-read level indicator helps parents find the right position for accurate installation and optimal safety.
  • Plush inserts keep your child comfortable on your many journeys together.
  • EPS, energy-absorbing foam for effective impact energy management.
  • Two integrated cup holders keep your child's drinks close at hand.
  • Kylie fashion: For a style that's just plain fun, the cool Kylie fashion fits the bill! Solids of bright hot pink, dove gray, charcoal and jet black keep this style modern and sleek.

Zaron Oil Control Mineral Loose Powder with SPF 30

The hot Lagos sun and sweat makes it hard to maintain that picture- perfect- face we wish we can carry the whole day! Here are some tips to maintain a sweat- free, oily-free face, in this Hot Lagos Weather!

  • Tone down on face creams and moisturizers. Rather use light facial moisturizer with SPF to protect from sun’s rays.
  • NO! No stick and cream foundation because they can be heavy for the hot weather, rather use liquid or any water based foundation and loose powder which is lighter and leaves your skin oil-free.
  • When you sweat, don’t rub your face. Gently dab your face with a blotting paper.
  • To re-touch your face with powder, use a makeup brush instead of a makeup sponge.

Fast growing cosmetics brand, Zaron Cosmetics has introduced a new range of blush; Zaron Hyper Blush; the new blush collection features highly pigmented individual matte blushes.

Blush should add natural colour to the cheeks and help define the face but this is usually not the case as darker -people usually have issues picking out the right blush fr their skintone but with the brand's latest collection, there is a colour for every skintone.

The new range features highly and beatifully pigmented blush colours to brighten the face, they are matte so they work perfect for all skin types.

 

If there is any part of makeup art I've been loving in the past 3 years, it's blush. I never really understood the concept of blush until I accidentally found the perfect shade for me and applied it perfectly. Since then, I've been very experimental with it. I can do without eyeshadow and replace a lip colour with lip balm but I never miss my blush.

 
Pink blush however is one colour I've never quite tried before and that is irking because apparently a darker shade of pink suits my skin colour beautifully right along with this Pink blush I got from Zaron Makeup. 
 
With all my multi-tasking instincts in full gear, I tested this product in varying capacities and it excelled when I used it as:
 
  1. Eyeshadow: when applied in a pressing motion on a good base or primer, this pink shade really pops. It is a matte pink colour which is especially beautiful on much fairer skin tones than mine but I don't mind all the same. I also use it as a transition colour sometimes and it gives off the ever so slight pink colour which in no way overwhelms the prominent colour.
  2. Lip Colour: yes, lip colour. Because this product is super pigmented, it shows up anywhere it is placed. What I do is to make sure my lips are moist and use the pad of my finger to directly dab this product onto my lips. I can deepen the intensity simply by applying more colour. The best part? It ends up as a matte lip and you know how I love my matte products.
  3. Blush: lol, yes a blush. That's what it was meant to be right so definitely a blush. I use an angled brush to apply the product directly to the apples of my cheeks and then I blend backwards. A faint flush is usually fine but every once in a while, I want some more and so I use some more.
There you have it - the 3 ways I use the Zaron Hyperblush in Electric Crush.
Is there any other way you'd rather use this product? I'd love to hear about it.

Damiana extract: 
Damiana, also known as turnera diffusa, is a shrub native to the Americas. This is an extraordinary herb with the natural power to support the urinary tract and the sexual system. The leaf is the part of the plant typically used in supplements. This herb is also beneficial for boosting mental and physical stamina.

The maintenance of a healthy immune system is one important aspect of maintaining overall wellness. Nature's nutrients can be especially helpful in optimizing your immune system. Over centuries of traditional use and decades of modern scientific validation, one food has emerged as perhaps the greatest immune-supporter: the humble mushroom.

Supreme Immune Booster contains a time-tested, extensively-researched mushroom extract that supports peak immune system health – for strong defenses you can count on.

Supreme Immune Booster features coriolus versicolor extract, also known as trametes versicolor, a mushroom that is so highly regarded for its wellness benefits, its sales reach hundreds of millions of dollars annually in Asia. This fungi has been the subject of much study in the Far East, where research has focused on two compounds: polysaccharide-K (Krestin, PSK) and polysaccharide peptide (PSP), which both exhibit notable immune-supportive properties. 

Studies have shown that coriolus versicolor and its polysaccharides contain notable levels of antioxidants. These antioxidants scavenge free radicals, which are produced by immune cells, among other sources. While a normal amount of free radicals isn't necessarily problematic, an abundance of them can negatively affect immunity. As they take out harmful excessive free radicals, the antioxidants of Supreme Immune Booster aid the immune system and help to maintain overall wellbeing.

Polysaccharides, are carbohydrate molecules with long structures that have been shown to assist in modulating the body's immune responses, functioning as “directors” in optimizing this complex and all-important body system. Researchers have suggested that coriolus versicolor-derived polysaccharides PSK and PSP, found in Supreme Immune Booster, appear to positively influence the activity of immune cells while modulating the body’s immune response.

Green tea consumption dates back more than 4000 years ago in China. Tea use expanded to Japan around the 6th century. Green tea is now becoming more common in the West, where black tea has traditionally been consumed.

Bermuda grass has many medicinal properties and benefits, such as antimicrobial and antiviral properties. It is also a great detoxifier and can maintain alkalinity of your blood.

Preparation: Measure, into a pot, enough water for the number of large cups (8oz/250ml) you want to make and add 2 heaping teaspoons per cup. Add 25% more water to compensate for evaporation. Make enough for a few days if you like. When you scoop out the tea, scoop deep down into the bag to make sure the tea is kept well mixed. Example: If you want to prepare 4 cups of tea, measure 5 cups of water and 8 heaping teaspoons of tea. Heat on a stove until boiling, then turn stove off or set to low and allow to simmer for 10 minutes. Stir and allow the tea to cool, then strain into a pitcher. For best results let it soak for a few hours or overnight before straining. Store the pitcher in the refrigerator and drink the tea cold or re-heated. CLEAR ESSENCE SKIN BEAUTIFYING BODY MILK
MAXI TONE - 8 oz.

 

CLEAR ESSENCE SKIN BEAUTIFYING MILK For Maximum Even Skin Tone and Smoother Skin All Over Body Complexion Lotion.

 

PURPOSE:

Skin Lightener


USES:
For an even toned glow by fading away skin discolorations such as age spots, freckles, or dark patches that may occur from pregnancy or the use of birth control pills.


WHEN USING THIS PRODUCT:
* Avoid contact with eyes
* Avoid unnecessary sun exposure and use a suncreen to prevent darkening from recurring
* Test overnight on inside of elbow before use
* If skin irritation occurs, discontinue use and consult a doctor
* Keep out of reach of children. If swallowed, seek medical assistance.


DIRECTIONS
* Spread a thin layer into patches on face, hands arms or body.
* Use twice daily or as directed by a doctor and in 4-6 weeks the effect should be evident.
* Not for use on children under 12 except on doctor's instructions.


OTHER INFORMATION:
Close lid tightly after each use. Product may darken when exposed to air.
This will not affect performance or safety. -

ACTIVE INGREDIENT:
Hydroquinone, 2.0%2

Possible to set the order in 3 colors: blue, green and pink (toothpaste is the same in every color version offered separately)

Toothpaste with xylitol to prevent dental caries. Gentle formula cleans and protects the milk teeth. It contains fluorine. Toothpaste with strawberry flavor for children from 12 months.

Toothbrush with a small round head, tapered, soft bristle gently cleans the teeth and gums of the child. The shape of the brush helps to reach up to the back teeth. The handle is wide, soft and protected from sliding out. With plastic, hygienic cap on the brush head.

Pouch for storing toothbrushes and toothpaste.

 

Warning!

The kit is designed for children over 12 months.

Offer applies to a single set in one selected color version.

Older versions of the product may contain a toothpaste without fluoride.

 

Under the new recommendations of the 2014 years of the American Dental Association, fluoridated toothpaste at a concentration of 1000 ppm F must be administered in an amount equivalent to:

  • "Grain of rice" - children under 3 years of age,
  • "Pea" for children ages 3 - 6 years.

According to the American Dental Association fluoride treatment it is safe both in prophylaxis and in checking caries.

It features a toybar that can be used in 2 positions helping enhance babies tactile, hearing and visual skills. The walker has a well padded seat and can be adjusted in height to suit the build of different children ensuring that their feet touch the floor correctly The Walky Talky Walker also has front swivel wheels making it easier for baby to guide themselves around and safety brakes called “stoppers” which stop the structure when reaching a step. The play panel is detachable to play also when not in the baby walker.

Group 0+ Car Seats: You should keep a baby in a group 0+ rear-facing car seat for as long as possible as this is the safest way of transporting your baby in the car. You should only move them onto the next car seat once they have reached the weight limit of that seat, or the crown of their head is level with the top of the car seat. The weight limits may vary so please ensure you have read the labels on the side of the seat which will tell you your specific seats limits.

Suitability: When buying a car seat its important to make sure you are choosing the correct one for both your car and your child. It’s important you select the correct type of car seat for your child’s weight and because not all car seats will fit all cars it is critical that you check the selected car seat will fit your model of car. Follow the instructions provided with your chosen seat carefully for a safe and accurate fitting of the car seat and make sure you have the instructions to hand for future reference. Your car manual will also provide guidance on any fitting guidance specific to that car model.

Free Car Seat Demonstration In Store: All our Babies R Us stores have advisors trained to fit car seats and check that the car seat you are considering is the right one for your car and your child. They will happily demonstrate how to fit it safely. We offer this securefit service because we know how important it is to keep your child safe on all your car journeys.

Graco's 4Ever All-in-One Car Seat, in Kylie, gives you 10 years with one car seat. It's comfortable for your child and convenient for you as it transitions from rear-facing in a harness for your infant (4 - 40 lbs.) to a forward-facing, five-point harness seat (20 - 65 lbs.) to a high-back, belt-positioning booster (30 - 100 lbs.) to a backless, belt-positioning booster (40 - 120 lbs.). For a proper fit, the Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System and 10-position headrest let you adjust the harness and headrest together, with no rethreading. The six-position recline keeps your child comfortable, while the InRight™ LATCH system with one-second attachment makes installation easy. It's the only seat that truly goes from baby to booster!

Zaron Oil Control Mineral Loose Powder with SPF 30

Protects skin from the sun, provides sheer natural coverage to set make up, softens color and smooth the texture of skin.

The hot Lagos sun and sweat makes it hard to maintain that picture- perfect- face we wish we can carry the whole day! Here are some tips to maintain a sweat- free, oily-free face, in this Hot Lagos Weather!

  • Tone down on face creams and moisturizers. Rather use light facial moisturizer with SPF to protect from sun’s rays.
  • NO! No stick and cream foundation because they can be heavy for the hot weather, rather use liquid or any water based foundation and loose powder which is lighter and leaves your skin oil-free.
  • When you sweat, don’t rub your face. Gently dab your face with a blotting paper.
  • To re-touch your face with powder, use a makeup brush instead of a makeup sponge.

Fast growing cosmetics brand, Zaron Cosmetics has introduced a new range of blush; Zaron Hyper Blush; the new blush collection features highly pigmented individual matte blushes.

Blush should add natural colour to the cheeks and help define the face but this is usually not the case as darker -people usually have issues picking out the right blush fr their skintone but with the brand's latest collection, there is a colour for every skintone.

The new range features highly and beatifully pigmented blush colours to brighten the face, they are matte so they work perfect for all skin types.

 

If there is any part of makeup art I've been loving in the past 3 years, it's blush. I never really understood the concept of blush until I accidentally found the perfect shade for me and applied it perfectly. Since then, I've been very experimental with it. I can do without eyeshadow and replace a lip colour with lip balm but I never miss my blush.

 
Pink blush however is one colour I've never quite tried before and that is irking because apparently a darker shade of pink suits my skin colour beautifully right along with this Pink blush I got from Zaron Makeup. 
 
With all my multi-tasking instincts in full gear, I tested this product in varying capacities and it excelled when I used it as:
 
  1. Eyeshadow: when applied in a pressing motion on a good base or primer, this pink shade really pops. It is a matte pink colour which is especially beautiful on much fairer skin tones than mine but I don't mind all the same. I also use it as a transition colour sometimes and it gives off the ever so slight pink colour which in no way overwhelms the prominent colour.
  2. Lip Colour: yes, lip colour. Because this product is super pigmented, it shows up anywhere it is placed. What I do is to make sure my lips are moist and use the pad of my finger to directly dab this product onto my lips. I can deepen the intensity simply by applying more colour. The best part? It ends up as a matte lip and you know how I love my matte products.
  3. Blush: lol, yes a blush. That's what it was meant to be right so definitely a blush. I use an angled brush to apply the product directly to the apples of my cheeks and then I blend backwards. A faint flush is usually fine but every once in a while, I want some more and so I use some more.
There you have it - the 3 ways I use the Zaron Hyperblush in Electric Crush.
Is there any other way you'd rather use this product? I'd love to hear about it.

 03 Violetta: a medium purple

Chasteberry (vitex agnus-castus) is also known as chaste tree. This herb is also known as “the women’s herb” and is native to the Mediterranean region and Western Asia. For many years chasteberry has been used successfully to quell PMS symptoms as well as to support menstrual irregularities. Chasteberry has also been used historically for its anti-parasitic properties.

Damiana extract: 
Damiana, also known as turnera diffusa, is a shrub native to the Americas. This is an extraordinary herb with the natural power to support the urinary tract and the sexual system. The leaf is the part of the plant typically used in supplements. This herb is also beneficial for boosting mental and physical stamina.

The maintenance of a healthy immune system is one important aspect of maintaining overall wellness. Nature's nutrients can be especially helpful in optimizing your immune system. Over centuries of traditional use and decades of modern scientific validation, one food has emerged as perhaps the greatest immune-supporter: the humble mushroom.

Supreme Immune Booster contains a time-tested, extensively-researched mushroom extract that supports peak immune system health – for strong defenses you can count on.

Supreme Immune Booster features coriolus versicolor extract, also known as trametes versicolor, a mushroom that is so highly regarded for its wellness benefits, its sales reach hundreds of millions of dollars annually in Asia. This fungi has been the subject of much study in the Far East, where research has focused on two compounds: polysaccharide-K (Krestin, PSK) and polysaccharide peptide (PSP), which both exhibit notable immune-supportive properties. 

Studies have shown that coriolus versicolor and its polysaccharides contain notable levels of antioxidants. These antioxidants scavenge free radicals, which are produced by immune cells, among other sources. While a normal amount of free radicals isn't necessarily problematic, an abundance of them can negatively affect immunity. As they take out harmful excessive free radicals, the antioxidants of Supreme Immune Booster aid the immune system and help to maintain overall wellbeing.

Polysaccharides, are carbohydrate molecules with long structures that have been shown to assist in modulating the body's immune responses, functioning as “directors” in optimizing this complex and all-important body system. Researchers have suggested that coriolus versicolor-derived polysaccharides PSK and PSP, found in Supreme Immune Booster, appear to positively influence the activity of immune cells while modulating the body’s immune response.

 

Ingredients: Coriolus versicolor extract (Trametes versicolor) (40% polysaccharides) 500 mg. This healthy mushroom is also known as turkey tails

Green tea consumption dates back more than 4000 years ago in China. Tea use expanded to Japan around the 6th century. Throughout Asia, green tea is an extremely popular beverage and is historically known as a natural remedy for whatever ails you. Modern medicinal research is providing a scientific basis for this belief. Promising data showing disease-preventive effects of green tea from cell-culture and human studies have emerged. Green Tea consumption has now been shown to be useful for maintenance of cardiovascular and metabolic health. Green tea is now becoming more common in the West, where black tea has traditionally been consumed.
 
Bell Japanese Green Tea is processed differently than other teas. The leaves are steamed immediately after plucking and then dried. This ensures that you enjoy a mild, sweet tasting tea, packed with super nutrients.

Here is some brief information on a few of the herbs in the tea:

Uva-ursi (Arctostaphylos uva-ursi), also known as bear’s grape, is used in traditional herbal medicine for treatment of early symptoms of mild urinary tract infections such as burning sensation during urination and/or frequent urination. The leaf is the medicinal part of the plant used in this formulation.

Stinging Nettle (Urtica dioica) is a flowering plant traditionally used in herbal medicine as a diuretic. Austria has a long history of using stinging nettle to support the kidneys, urinary tract and cardiovascular system. Stinging nettle has more than fifty naturally occurring chemicals present and the leaves are high in flavonol glycosides such as quercetin, which is a great antioxidant.

Bermuda Grass (Cynodon dactylon) is a perennial grass from the family Poaceae. This grass is abundant in India and Africa, but also grows in many tropical countries. Bermuda grass has many medicinal properties and benefits, such as antimicrobial and antiviral properties. It is also a great detoxifier and can maintain alkalinity of your blood.

The Kidney Cleanse & Function Tea comes as a loose tea, so you can make an entire pot at one time if you prefer and it is a 2-4 week supply for a very reasonable price. If you want to support and maintain sound kidney health, this tea is exactly what you’ve been looking for.

Preparation: Measure, into a pot, enough water for the number of large cups (8oz/250ml) you want to make and add 2 heaping teaspoons per cup. Add 25% more water to compensate for evaporation. Make enough for a few days if you like. When you scoop out the tea, scoop deep down into the bag to make sure the tea is kept well mixed. Example: If you want to prepare 4 cups of tea, measure 5 cups of water and 8 heaping teaspoons of tea. Heat on a stove until boiling, then turn stove off or set to low and allow to simmer for 10 minutes. Stir and allow the tea to cool, then strain into a pitcher. For best results let it soak for a few hours or overnight before straining. Store the pitcher in the refrigerator and drink the tea cold or re-heated. You can put some in a thermos to take along with you to work. The tea has a pleasing aroma. The tea tastes great without sugar or sweeteners. If you prefer a sweeter tasting tea, use a little bit of honey or stevia. Do not prepare the tea by pouring hot water over it, as this will not give you the full benefit.

Our sterilizer is easy to use thanks to only one button to start the cycle. It is practical, compact and easy to use.

  • Effectively eliminates harmful bacteria with the power of steam, kills up to 99.9% of harmful household germs

Close to You ergonomicbaby carrier can be used in 3 different position, following the growth of your child. It can be used from birth since 15 kg and it ensures stability and comfort for each situations.

configurations.

Parent – facing position for the first months, forward – facing position for elder babies and backpack for 12 months old children. Close to You adapts to your child’s growth, ensuring utmost comfort and ergonomic shapes for your baby and for you during each step of growth.

Product description

Chicco Kit toothbrush + toothpaste + case + 12m for the first milk teeth.

Set consisting of toothbrush, toothpaste strawberry and cases, and put it upon form good habits regarding oral health of the child.

Possible to set the order in 3 colors: blue, green and pink (toothpaste is the same in every color version offered separately)

Toothpaste with xylitol to prevent dental caries. Gentle formula cleans and protects the milk teeth. It contains fluorine. Toothpaste with strawberry flavor for children from 12 months.

Toothbrush with a small round head, tapered, soft bristle gently cleans the teeth and gums of the child. The shape of the brush helps to reach up to the back teeth. The handle is wide, soft and protected from sliding out. With plastic, hygienic cap on the brush head.

Pouch for storing toothbrushes and toothpaste.

 

Warning!

The kit is designed for children over 12 months.

Offer applies to a single set in one selected color version.

Older versions of the product may contain a toothpaste without fluoride.

 

Under the new recommendations of the 2014 years of the American Dental Association, fluoridated toothpaste at a concentration of 1000 ppm F must be administered in an amount equivalent to:

  • "Grain of rice" - children under 3 years of age,
  • "Pea" for children ages 3 - 6 years.

According to the American Dental Association fluoride treatment it is safe both in prophylaxis and in checking caries.

New Simplicity stroller

The new SimpliCity stroller is stylish, light, comfortable and versatile. This is why it’s the ideal stroller for busy urban life, shopping or travelling, without problems. Suitable from birth, the comfortable seat fully reclines and features a 5 point safety harness equipped with shoulder and crotch strap pads. The light aluminium frame, one-piece height adjustable handle and lockable front swivel wheels make the stroller very agile. The included folding hood protects baby from the bad weather. Simple to open and close. Once closed it’s very compact and freestanding with a useful carry handle on the side.The SimpliCity can be turned in to a useful travel system with the addition of the Chicco Key Fit group 0+ child car seat, available separately. The car seat clips simply and easily into the stroller seat locking securely.

You can have easy control over the stroller

This baby pram comes with a padded and large handle, which is easily adjustable. You can, thus, have easy grip over it and steer it with little or almost no effort. In addition, the stroller has swivel wheels, which help in guiding the pram without any problem. You can push the pram easily along a rough path, because of these swivel wheels. Furthermore, you can also stop the stroller without any problem because there is a wheel brake situated close to the wheels at the back. You can operate this brake with the help of your foot.

This stroller is good for protecting your child from bad weather

Taking your kid out for a walk is no longer going to be a problem, if you have this Chicco stroller. It comes with various advantageous features, which are enough to protect your baby from harsh weather conditions. There is a large sun shade, which helps in keeping the harmful ultraviolet rays of the sun out of your little one's eyes. There is a rain cover, which helps in protecting your baby from a sudden drizzle.

The stroller is safe and comfortable

This baby stroller is not only comfortable, but also safe. It has a completely padded seat and extra padded wings on the sides to protect your little angel's head. In addition, it has an adjustable back rest.
